These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ebony, yellow, turquise
House: townhouse, colonial, tower, palace
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, oliveros, pall-mall, swisher
 1. the colonial house is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
 2. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
 3. the swisher-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the townhouse house is not to the left of the palace house##8
 5. the blend-smoker is not to the right of the blend-smoker##8
 6. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the palace house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person who likes turquise is between the oliveros-smoker and the colonial house##2
 9. the swisher-smoker is the person who likes yellow##1
10. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person who likes yellow is not to the left of the swisher-smoker##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the pall-mall-smoker##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the colonial house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Color   | ebony | turquise   | fuchsia   | yellow  |
| House         | colonial  | tower  | palace  | townhouse |
| Cigar     | blend    | pall-mall | oliveros     | swisher    |

