.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, german, malaysian, turkish
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, monopoly, bridge
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blue, purple, ivory
 1. the fan of salsa is between the person who likes aquamarine and the fan of indie##2
 2. the german is not to the right of the person who likes blue##8
 3. the german is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 4. the italian is not to the right of the person who likes ivory##8
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the turkish##8
 7. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
 8. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the person who likes blue##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
11. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the turkish is on the left of the german##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
17. the italian is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person playing whist is not to the right of the person who likes blue##8
19. the turkish is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality      | italian | malaysian | turkish  | german  |
| Game          | bridge     | whist | backgammon | monopoly  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Color           | purple | ivory | aquamarine    | blue  |

