The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, blues, punk, pop
 1. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
 2. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8
 3. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8
 4. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 5. the fan of punk is the nigerian##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the thai##6
 8. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the fan of punk and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
 9. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
10. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
11. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
12. the owner of the bird is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
14. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
15. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Flower      | balloon-flower    | amaryllis   | bellflower        | daisy  |
