11. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
13. the person traveling to berlin is not to the left of the chef##8
14. the doctor is not to the right of the writer##8
15. the doctor is the person who likes apricot##1
16. the fisherman is not to the right of the person who likes green##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Job           | fisherman | doctor       | chef      | writer  |
| Color   | ebony    | apricot | green   | mauve   |
| Sport   | tennis   | surfing          | volleyball      | cricket  |
| City   | nizza   | venice      | san-francisco | berlin |

